<ul>
<li>Amato, Carol A. (2002). <i><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://books.google.com/books?id=E9I0P5wyAAYC">Backyard Pets: Activities for Exploring Wildlife Close to Home</a></i>. John Wiley and Sons. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0471416932" class="internal mw-magiclink-isbn">ISBN 0-471-41693-2</a>.</li>
