<li>Christian, Peter D. and Scotti, Paul D. (1998). <i>Picornalike Viruses of Insects</i>, in: Miller, Lois K. et al. (1998). <i><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://books.google.com/books?id=QAwsTrfwSgMC">The Insect Virus</a></i>. Springer. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0306458810" class="internal mw-magiclink-isbn">ISBN 0-306-45881-0</a>.</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Jean-Henri_Fabre" title="Jean-Henri Fabre">Fabre, Jean-Henri</a> (1943 ed.). <i><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://books.google.com/books?id=uwnuQcdqFTMC">Social Life in the Insect World</a></i>. Pelican books. Reprint: <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/9781603034883" class="internal mw-magiclink-isbn">ISBN 978-1-60303-488-3</a>.</li>
<li>Finch, Betty and Zhang, Guojun (2006). <i><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://books.google.com/books?id=nVhEksxiU0IC">The Immortal Molded Gourds of Mr. Zhang Cairi</a></i>. Betty Finch. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0970033850" class="internal mw-magiclink-isbn">ISBN 0-9700338-5-0</a>.</li>
